    "body": "Ok I think this is not a bug. just because how PowerShell work on Windows.\n\nhttps://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_parsing?view=powershell-7.5#tilde-\n\nhttps://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/powershell/scripting/learn/experimental-features?view=powershell-7.5#psnativewindowstildeexpansion\n\n> On non-Windows platforms, tilde expansion is handled natively\n\nTherefore, we should update the documentation for the preset command.\nAdd a new line for PowerShell users\n```pwsh\nstarship preset jetpack -o $HOME/.config/starship.toml #PowerShell\n```\n",
